                        "CAP: under a network partition you must choose Consistent OR Available; the 'pick 2 of 3' framing is misleading and CAP is narrow (only linearizability + partitions).",
                        "Many systems drop linearizability for performance, not fault tolerance — its latency is proportional to network-delay uncertainty (Attiya & Welch).",
