                        "Windows: tumbling (disjoint), hopping (overlapping), sliding (relative), session (activity-gap).",
                        "Three joins: stream-stream (windowed), stream-table (enrichment via a local CDC-maintained copy), table-table (changelog-to-materialized-view).",
